Hi Agent Orange,
<p>
I'm going through your website and feel like my thoughts and feelings about
AA are staring me in the face. I think it's fascinating that you put up this
website and I'm sure you have helped a lot of people see the light.

<p>

I came back into AA in March this year and got a sponsor that stopped
talking to me because I wasn't doing the 9th step fast enough. She's
unemployed and didn't really consider the fact that I'm a single mom and
have to work almost 11 hrs. a day. So doing all the steps in one week is
what I was supposed to do on top of my responsibilities. I crashed and went
into depression when I realized that a lot of other people were ignoring me
after a while, because I didn't do it their ways.

