<p>
<font color="blue">
Hi John,
<p>
Thanks for the letter.

<p>
Yes, I quit drinking, and quit smoking too, by doing it pretty much my own way.
I had smoked for more than 30 years, and drank for almost 20,
and I have about 5 3/4 years off of both now. Oh happy day.
<p>
(See the
<a href="orange-intro.html">introduction to the web site</a>
for the story of my start down the road to sobriety.)
<p>
But I do not <i>*recommend*</i> going it alone, in spite of the fact that
<a href="orange-effectiveness.html#Harvard_Mental">
the Harvard Medical School reported</a> that 80% of the successful quitters did it alone,
on their own.

